    "Table 2: The table compares GPT-3.5's performance when playing with Random and Danzero+ in different positions in Guandan environments over 30 games, with 15 rounds played in each of the two positions.",
    "To overcome these limitations and improve the model's performance, we introduced the action recommender tool as a crucial part of our approach.",
    "Results Analysis (1) ToM planning method outperforms Vanilla planning method: Table 1 shows that injecting belief knowledge obtained through ToM planning consistently improves the performance of almost all models.",
    "This highlights the importance of ToM knowledge in playing card games.",
    "Moreover, it is clear that LLM-agent has a natural ability to analyze other players' beliefs, and developing this skill dramatically contributes to its overall performance."
